{"_id":"T0KGsoctGFXp3MaJ","name":"Rules Quick Reference","content":"<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Victory Levels</strong></span></p>\n<p>Level 1 Victory: +1 Minor Wound; Stagger; Enter Close Combat</p>\n<p>Level 2 Victory: +1 Medium Wound; Disarm; Any Lower Outcome</p>\n<p>Level 3 Victory: +1 Serious Injury; Trip; Any Lower Outcome</p>\n<p>Level 4 Victory: +1 Fatal Injury; Dismember + 1 Serious Injury; Any Lower Outcome</p>\n<p>Level 5 Victory: Instant Death; Any Lower Outcome</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Close Combat</strong></span></p>\n<p>-Armor is ignored.</p>\n<p>-Characters using medium or larger weapons are considered unarmed.</p>\n<p>-Exception to above rule: One combatant is using a reach weapon, if so a medium weapon can be used.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Dual Wielding</strong></span></p>\n<p>Small Secondary Weapon = +2D6</p>\n<p>Medium Secondary Weapon = +1D6</p>\n<p>-Requires proficiency in both main and secondary weapon</p>\n<p>-Proficiency from secondary weapon not counted.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Combat Modifiers</strong></span></p>\n<p>High Ground = +2D6</p>\n<p>-Arguably inaccurate for one on one combat. </p>\n<p>Flank = +2D6</p>\n<p>-Bonus awarded for attacking a preoccupied opponent</p>\n<p>Staggered = -2D6</p>\n<p>-Lasts a round, status effect.</p>\n<p>Off Guard = CL in lieu of defense</p>\n<p>-CL determined by Narrator</p>\n<p>Prone = -4D6</p>\n<p>-Penalty for being prone during attack. Must take action to get up.</p>\n<p>Charge = +1D6</p>\n<p>-If at large distance, charge can be used to \"gain momentum\" on an attack.</p>\n<p>Brace = +2 wins against a charge</p>\n<p>-Higher reflex characters can use this to brace against a charge coming at them.</p>\n<p>Incapacitated = CL1 to obtain a level 5 victory</p>\n<p>-If a character doesn't have any dice to roll, or are otherwise incapacitated, the attacking character must achieve a CL of 1 with the result being a level 5 victory, disregarding armor and other stats.</p>\n<p><em>Homebrew</em></p>\n<p>Mounted Charge = +3D6</p>\n<p>-If doing a charge while mounted on something faster than running speed, gain extra dice.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Hardcore Rules</strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>Armor</strong></p>\n<p>Half players armor level (rounded down) is subtracted from their combat roll.</p>\n<p>Armor calculated per piece.</p>\n<p><strong>Weapon Dice Calculation</strong></p>\n<p><em>Size</em></p>\n<p>Small = +0D6, +0 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p>Medium = +1D6, +1 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p>Large = +2D6, +2 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p>Reach = +3D6, +3 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p><em>Type</em></p>\n<p>Hafted = +1D6</p>\n<p>Blunted = -1D6, +3 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p>Bladed = +1 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p>Speared = +1D6, +1 Armor Reduction</p>\n<p><strong>Ranged Rules</strong></p>\n<table style=\"width:99.1477%;height:93px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:15px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:15px\"> </td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:15px\">Stationary</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:15px\">50% Cover</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:15px\">90% Cover</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:15px\">\n<p>Moving <br />(Running Speed)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:15px\">Moving <br />(Fast Speed)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:16px\">Adjacent 0-5 Meters/0-16.4 Feet</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:16px\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:16px\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:16px\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:16px\">N/A</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:16px\">N/A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:14px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:14px\">Close 5-10 Meters/16.4-32.8 Feet</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:14px\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:14px\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:14px\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:14px\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:14px\">8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:16px\">Medium 10-50 Meters/32.8-164 Feet</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:16px\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:16px\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:16px\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:16px\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:16px\">8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:16px\">Long 50-100 Meters/164-328 Feet</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:16px\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:16px\">10</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:16px\">14</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:16px\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:16px\">10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:35.1513%;height:16px\">Sniper 100-1k Meters/328-3280 Feet</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3226%;height:16px\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3202%;height:16px\">10</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.7652%;height:16px\">14</td>\n<td style=\"width:18.0168%;height:16px\">8</td>\n<td style=\"width:13.1345%;height:16px\">10</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Moving towards/away from attacker counts as stationary.</p>\n<p>Moving targets in cover have the CL's added up.</p>\n<p>Slower than running speed counts as stationary.</p>\n<p>CL's doubled if shooter is moving during the same round.</p>\n<p>Sniper Range can only be attempted if weapon is scoped, shooter has proficiency in sniping, and isn't moving.</p>\n<p>Scoped Weapons CL at medium and long ranges are calculated as if at close range.</p>\n<p> </p>","img":null,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":2,"mYjx68T8K5Y7LRIo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.KblwEqp2oHT8wFTy"}}}
